  ('aboriginal-0a2fc18c-moex-00088', 'aboriginal-0a2fc18c', 'aboriginal-0a2fc18c-moex-112-47ce9a40', 'sub-aboriginal-0a2fc18c-06', NULL, 'essay', '假設某一小國為保護其稻農，擬對稻米施行進口配額（importquota）或
